{"tid":1082710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜見「中聯辦」可能被罰50萬,  台中攤商市民捐錢力挺","createTime":"2019-03-29T06:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T01:06:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5bae73ebc3dd4215c62e41407a08b5fce640c1c2","tid":1082710,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/story/6656/3725854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3725854&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=ab99bd64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/story/6656/3725854</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜見中聯辦罰50萬？台中攤商捐錢挺賣菜郎選總統<br />\n2019-03-29 11:06 &nbsp;聯合報 記者趙容萱╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜會晤港澳中聯辦主任，外傳陸委會指韓恐違反《兩岸人民關係條例》，最高罰50萬元罰鍰。<strong>台中市議員李麗華議員因應攤商、市井小民、婆婆媽媽要求，發起「一人500元，緊急救賣菜郎」，吸引逾百人到場參與力挺，捐出500、1000元，並喊「挺韓總、選總統！」「挺韓總、救台灣！」「台灣安全、人民有錢！」</strong><br />\n<br />\n台中市議員李麗華說，服務處近日接到無數來自夜市攤商、小販還有婆婆媽媽的聲援電話，表示要支持高雄市長韓國瑜，當他的最強後盾，韓市長才剛當選就已經開始為台灣農產品不遺餘力，做到「貨出去、人進來，台灣發大財」，短短七天就取得52億訂單，執政黨卻用盡方法打壓他，小百姓們直說「看不下去了！」希望一起幫韓市長，做韓市長的後盾。<br />\n<br />\n台中市議員李麗華指出，今天逾百名攤商、市井小民、婆婆媽媽放下手邊的工作，到場參與力挺韓市長，並且發出基層聲音，高雄市長韓國瑜出國拚訂單，是賺錢的金雞母，盼中央能重視，別再打壓賣菜郎。<br />\n<br />\n羅姓鴨肉焿攤商說，攤商生意在近幾年因一例一休等因素，生意愈來愈不好，他力挺韓國瑜，支持「貨出去、人進來，台灣發大財」全力拚經濟的理念。"},{"pid":"194d2f28c193f565047edf12dabf8f95297218df","tid":1082710,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2014-10-18/656/20141018002673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2014-10-18%2F656%2F20141018002673.jpg&h=3967729b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"022631a4fa8d32b6037f9d3e59d25bc287bf44f4","tid":1082710,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台中市議員李麗華說，服務處近日接到無數來自夜市攤商、小販還有婆婆媽媽的聲援電話，表示要支持高雄市長韓國瑜，當他的最強後盾，韓市長才剛當選就已經開始為台灣農產品不遺餘力，做到「貨出去、人進來，台灣發大財」，短短七天就取得52億訂單，執政黨卻用盡方法打壓他，小百姓們直說「看不下去了！」希望一起幫韓市長，做韓市長的後盾。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://na.cx/i/VBYeFUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBYeFUG.jpg&h=1499f2bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34c0937afb9ed0a88f1d8328b2b143bc54da813","tid":1082710,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"台中發大財"},{"pid":"db2424e55564a7f16d3adc3abc07b804aa6c2c78","tid":1082710,"uid":59838,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"港台都係俾老一輩上一代害撚死<br />\n<br />\n睇嘢咁短視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04687f01ae44a099d9a6509092866232306a245d","tid":1082710,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b34c0937afb9ed0a88f1d8328b2b143bc54da813","tid":1082710,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"台中發大財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac0630bf4f522b08805cb2dfb6b9aa2eaa3c52c","tid":1082710,"uid":60545,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"賣台發大財！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d35afec504b4d631c4c844a2f0d91d57d0c64","tid":1082710,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e26229b8bd1ccee01dad810e034976a9fcd763c","tid":1082710,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"小財唔出大財唔入"},{"pid":"337cd48d8779cfed6d1b49b9d0f30911d77aa0af","tid":1082710,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T